tags: Treatment satisfaction,
review: I visited Dr Tabrez for having dental implant. DR Tabrez was very friendly at the same time very professional. I had watched videos regarding the procedure and was very apprehensive but DR Tabrez first evaluated my teeth gave me the options explained the course and then the procedure itself was so pleasant. The anesthesia was vey good, he let me close my mouth every minute it was the best dental experience that i had ever had. His wife Dr ameerah is also very pleasant and together they form a really good team. I highly recommend Dr Tabrez to anyone who needs work to be done on their teeth

I had a severe tooth ache and after a thorough examination  Dr Ameera advised a root canal treatment for the tooth, the procedure was super smooth and I didn't feel a thing during the whole treatment.

review: I took my 6 year old daughter for her cavities. A chocolate lover, she had 6 cavities. In a single sitting Dr Ameera was able to fill all of them. Dr Tabrez kept encouraging my daughter that you are a strong girl. The procedure went well. No tears were shed at all. She may need Route canal for one of her teeth and she is most excited to go back! Says it all. Thank you to the Team Swiss Dental Aesthetics.

I am really amazed at the results and I really appreciate the care and comfort provided by the doctor. I must say it‚Äôs a must visit place for all your dental needs.
